spell_list.description: Enhances the primary specialty healing abilities of a single priest ally. Reactive heals gain an additional healing trigger and additional heal amount, Regenerative heals increase in heal amount, and Wards have increased damage absorption. This spell also enhances the casting speed and reuse speed of beneficial spells cast by the ally.
